Name: endometrial hyperplasia
Definition: An uterine benign neoplasm that is characterized by excessive proliferation of the cells of the endometrium.

Name: uterine fibroid
Definition: An uterine benign neoplasm derived from the smooth muscle layer of the uterus.

Name: obsolete introverted personality
Definition: An uterine benign neoplasm derived from the smooth muscle layer of the uterus.

Name: endometrial stromal nodule
Definition: An uterine benign neoplasm that has_material_basis_in cells reminiscent of proliferative phase endometrial stroma.
